[
    "User admin logged in with password=secret",
    "User guest logged in with password=12345",
    "System check OK"
] >> logs.

new MaskPassword:
    @ >> msg.
    (msg & "password=") >> Contains >> has_pass.
    has_pass >> check:
        is true:
            (msg & "=") >> Split >> parts.
            parts[0] >+> "=***" >> Return.
        else:
            msg >> Return.
    ..
..

logs >~> MaskPassword >> masked.
"Masked logs:" >> Display.
masked >> Display.
